{"tid":1030193,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"［求教］京阪神奈十日遊應該買KANSAI THRU PASS定係KANSAI ONE PASS？","createTime":"2019-02-20T20:19:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-20T23:59:47.000Z","uid":153615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9a46aaf4338dee754c337e6a5eda83f8321db30d","tid":1030193,"uid":153615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T20:19:33.000Z","msg":"想知兩者使用範圍有咩唔同同埋邊個抵啲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2df68edf54f2d973688d649eca3ac5c81240f213","tid":1030193,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T23:57:12.000Z","msg":"Thru Pass 真係一張pass，一個價錢有效期內任搭(京、阪、兵庫、奈良、和歌山)大部份私鐵同巴士，但JR就冇份。<br />\n<br />\nOne Pass本體係一張ICOCA（八達通），只係外國人專用+某啲景點有優惠，但係都係要逐程車計錢。<br />\n<br />\n因為本質上係IC，其實One Pass可以係唔係都買咗先，反正可以下次再用。<br />\n<br />\n而Thru Pass，睇需求啦，唔知你行程好難答。"},{"pid":"a9e81b8d5374753f06b2a2241ed7793a5ddb9f40","tid":1030193,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T23:59:47.000Z","msg":"補充：Kansai One Pass = ICOCA =通用交通IC(你當八達通)，全日本有IC標誌都用得，例如你可以去福岡搭地鐵都用得返。"}]}